text.tspan: All empires will contain their own laws, rules, decisions, and form of government. This constitution shall state the universal laws
applying to all players and empires (INCLUDING THE CREATOR). The minimum shall be five meets for taxes and free supplies for
survival or ten meets. Taxes are five meets per week and automatically paid to the Creator on Fridays. Taxes ᴅᴏ ɴᴏᴛ have to be paid if
others/the empire is willing to pay it for you.
During this period, the person will not earn or lose money including taxes. The leave must be for over 2 weeks and the
person must declare when they come back before playing in real life. After this, you cannot leave for one month. The
destruction of buildings is strictly prohibited unless confirmed by all builders of the building. If one finds their buildings
destroyed, the have the right to sue players you suspect of griefing.
If one wishes to file a lawsuit against another person, the person must declare the court case and the date of the case.
If you can’t make it or are unsure, please declare of you will be fined 25 meets. The abbreviation for meets is “me.,”
